    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Aclees aenigmaticus sp. n. Paratype, China, Sichuan. Structure of the endophallus. bl = basal lobe; ul = upper lobe; mb = median branches; la = lateral arms; ll = lower lobe; h = hook; ap = apex of penis." ;
