    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Aclees aenigmaticus sp. n. Paratype, Taiwan. Penis, dorsal view (A), profile (E); apex of penis (C); everted endophallus, profile (G), dorsal view (I), frontal view (K). Aclees taiwanensis Kôno, 1933, Taiwan. Penis, dorsal view (B), profile (F); apex of penis (D); everted endophallus, profile (H), dorsal view (J), frontal view (L)." ;
